{"number":81,"name":"سُورَةُ التَّكۡوِيرِ","englishName":"At-Takwir","englishNameTranslation":"The Overthrowing","revelationType":"Meccan","ayahs":[{"number":5801,"text":"When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5802,"text":"And when the stars fall, dispersing,","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5803,"text":"And when the mountains are removed","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5804,"text":"And when full-term she-camels are neglected","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5805,"text":"And when the wild beasts are gathered","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5806,"text":"And when the seas are filled with flame","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5807,"text":"And when the souls are paired","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5808,"text":"And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5809,"text":"For what sin she was killed","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5810,"text":"And when the pages are made public","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5811,"text":"And when the sky is stripped away","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5812,"text":"And when Hellfire is set ablaze","numberInSurah":12,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5813,"text":"And when Paradise is brought near,","numberInSurah":13,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5814,"text":"A soul will [then] know what it has brought [with it].","numberInSurah":14,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5815,"text":"So I swear by the retreating stars -","numberInSurah":15,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5816,"text":"Those that run [their courses] and disappear -","numberInSurah":16,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5817,"text":"And by the night as it closes in","numberInSurah":17,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5818,"text":"And by the dawn when it breathes","numberInSurah":18,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5819,"text":"[That] indeed, the Qur'an is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger","numberInSurah":19,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5820,"text":"[Who is] possessed of power and with the Owner of the Throne, secure [in position],","numberInSurah":20,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5821,"text":"Obeyed there [in the heavens] and trustworthy.","numberInSurah":21,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5822,"text":"And your companion is not [at all] mad.","numberInSurah":22,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5823,"text":"And he has already seen Gabriel in the clear horizon.","numberInSurah":23,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5824,"text":"And Muhammad is not a withholder of [knowledge of] the unseen.","numberInSurah":24,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5825,"text":"And the Qur'an is not the word of a devil, expelled [from the heavens].","numberInSurah":25,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5826,"text":"So where are you going?","numberInSurah":26,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5827,"text":"It is not except a reminder to the worlds","numberInSurah":27,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5828,"text":"For whoever wills among you to take a right course.","numberInSurah":28,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5829,"text":"And you do not will except that Allah wills - Lord of the worlds.","numberInSurah":29,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":586,"ruku":523,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false}]}